                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-10 12:22:14',
                                   'sentence' => 'Red pepper has made three elementary mistakes (assumptions) 1) The common one that homosexuality is equal to sodomy (their shallow analogy of the ear above) 2) Following number 1 above that sodomy is practiced only by homosexuals and 3) That all homosexuals engage in anal sex.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 50,
