                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-10 12:22:14',
                                   'sentence' => 'It\'s worth noting, that from the very beginning sodomy and homosexuality were two categorically separate things.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 55,
                                   'stories_id' => 2,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '138'
                                 },
