                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-10 12:22:14',
                                   'sentence' => 'While gay and lesbian bloggers in Africa use blogs to express themselves freely, there are also anti gay bloggers targeting them.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 69,
                                   'stories_id' => 2,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '152'
